                <collation>
                  <p>The quires, signed with letters, are 16 in number, viz. 7 in the first part of the volume (<locus from="1" to="68">foll. 1—68</locus>), and 9 in the second part (<locus from="69" to="159">foll. 69—159</locus>).</p>
                </collation>
                <condition>
                  <list>
                    <item>
                      <p>Two of of the leaves, <locus from="119" to="119">foll. 119</locus> and <locus from="159" to="159">159</locus>, are much stained and torn.</p>
                    </item>
                  </list>
